name: Hilarie Burton / Peyton Sawyer
description:
An embedding of actress Hilarie Burton, mostly trained on images of her One Three Hill days. It can also serve as an embedding for the character of Peyton Sawyer, otherwise known as many teen boys' wet dream in the early 2000's.

512x512 or 512x768

For some reason, it's not easy to get good likeness at low weight. If you want to optimalize likeness I would put the weight of the embedding at 1.05 to 1.1, depending on the results you get.

30 steps DPM++ 2M KARRAS

CFG 6-7
